1 WHEREAS, in 2019, Chris co-founded Jewel of the South, a bar and restaurant that
2 quickly earned international acclaim and enjoys a near-permanent ranking in both The
3 World's 50 Best Bars and North America's 50 Best Bars lists; he and his team's authentic
4 approach to true Southern-style service earned the bar the Michter's Art of Hospitality
5 Award in 2024; and
6 WHEREAS, Chris was named the 2022 Spirited Awards U.S. Bartender of the Year,
7 and he most recently received the Roku Industry Icon Award as part of North America's 50
8 Best Bars 2026; and
9 WHEREAS, Chris Hannah is a titan of the hospitality and cocktail industries and is
10 most deserving of recognition for his outstanding career.
11 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
12 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Chris Hannah for his contributions to the
13 American bar industry and North American cocktail culture and does hereby extend sincere
14 wishes that he remain prosperous in all of his endeavors.
